{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/Ubuntu下nvm的安装使用/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"nvm介绍\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nvm%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\" aria-label=\"nvm介绍 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>nvm介绍</h2>\n<p>nvm是一个node版本管理器，类似与Python中的 <code class=\"language-text\">Anaconda</code> 、<code class=\"language-text\">virtural-env</code>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-label=\"安装 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装</h2>\n<p>nvm的github仓库地址为 <code class=\"language-text\">https://github.com/creationix/nvm</code></p>\n<p>项目的说明文档中列出了多种安装方式，选用其中一种进行安装。</p>\n<p>1.在终端执行以下命令，将自动进行nvm的安装：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.34.0/install.sh | bash</code></pre></div>\n<p>nvm将被安装到 <code class=\"language-text\">$HOME/.nvm</code> 目录中。</p>\n<p>2.安装完成后，执行以下命令查看是否安装完成：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvm --version</code></pre></div>\n<p>3.出现 <code class=\"language-text\">Command &#39;nvm&#39; not found</code> 的解决办法：</p>\n<p>关掉当前终端并重新打开一个新的窗口，问题解决。</p>\n<h2 id=\"使用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用</h2>\n<p>查看所有可供安装的node版本：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvm ls-remote</code></pre></div>\n<p>选择自己想要的版本进行安装，本人选用 <code class=\"language-text\">v11.11.0</code> 安装</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvm install v11.11.0</code></pre></div>\n<p>查看本地已安装的node：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvm ls</code></pre></div>\n<p>使用node：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvm use v11.11.0</code></pre></div>","excerpt":"nvm介绍 nvm是一个node版本管理器，类似与Python中的  、。 安装 nvm的github仓库地址为  项目的说明文档中列出了多种安装方式，选用其中一种进行安装。 1.在终端执行以下命令，将自动进行nvm的安装： nvm将被安装到  目录中。 2.安装完成后，执行以…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Ubuntu%E4%B8%8Bnvm%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/#nvm%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\">nvm介绍</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Ubuntu%E4%B8%8Bnvm%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">安装</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Ubuntu%E4%B8%8Bnvm%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">使用</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/Ubuntu下nvm的安装使用/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ubuntu下nvm的安装使用","date":"Jan 15, 2023","tags":["Linux","nvm"],"keywords":["Ivan Mao's Blog","Ivan Mao"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Ubuntu下nvm的安装使用/","series":[],"lastmod":"2023-01-15"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}